{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Additional pre-existing workflow-vs-bespoke parity nit (found in tepid-bus-pomp code review, orthogonal to {{plan}} fix): bespoke pass4_coach returns [] early on EMPTY surviving (0 advisories) → 0 coach LLM calls; the workflow ALWAYS runs the coach_notes prompt step → 1 coach call with an empty listing on a clean PASS. Pre-dates B5 (the coach step always ran since B2). Fold into the parity-hardening: gate the workflow coach_notes on surviving>0 (an if:/branch) so a 0-advisory PASS makes no coach call, matching bespoke."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782519601280302001,"uuid":"c0f367fd-549e-4ecc-8c1c-03c7f36592f2"}